longBusinessSummary: Job Solution Sweden Holding AB operates as a recruitment company in Sweden and Norway. It offers search and headhunting services for civil engineering, infrastructure, and industrial sectors. The company also provides IT and business development consulting services. Job Solution Sweden Holding AB was founded in 2015 and is based in Sundbyberg, Sweden.
